snippet.title: SurvivalScape Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Steam Trailer for my video game SurvivalScape

Can you survive? SurvivalScape is an auto shooter bullet hell where you can challenge your friends to highscores on the leaderboard. Kill enemies, collect crystals, and level up!

View on Itch.io: https://bearlikelion.itch.io/survivalscape
